 what’s involved in each step."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Many businesses ask, \"How fast can I get ISO 9001 certification?\" or \"Is there a quick ISO certification process available?\" The answer lies in how prepared your organization is. With expert support and a streamlined approach, some companies can complete certification in as little as 30 to 60 days. By understanding the average time to get ISO certified, you can set realistic goals and avoid costly delays. For organizations in the UAE, working with experienced consultants like WIZMS can help reduce the ISO certification time frame and ensure you meet all requirements efficiently."}]]}],["$","footer",null,{"className":"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"how fast can I get ISO 9001 certification"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"ISO 27001 certification duration for small businesses"}],["$","span","2",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"quick ISO certification process"}],["$","span","3",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"average time to get ISO certified"}],["$","span","4",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"ISO certification process timeline in UAE"}]]}]}]]}]}],[["$","script","script-0",{"src":"/_next/static/chunks/38753a6eced83920.js","async":true}]],["$","$L3",null,{"children":["$","$4",null,{"name":"Next.MetadataOutlet","children":"$@5"}]}]]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
